    Title: Yoga-Vasishtha
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Death=The Destruction of I-Consciousness
Commentary: |
  This is the Maharshi's method.
---
\‘What am I? What is the world?’ This enquiry into truth is a fire.
Burn up the false ‘I’ which identifies itself with the body in the
fire of enquiry. When this is accomplished, then the ‘I’ remains in
Atman.
